      <title>Behind the Design: How Gentler Streak approaches fitness with “humanity“</title>
      <link>https://n-kase.github.io/rss/posts/post-513/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 11:29:11 +0900</pubDate>
      
